{"word":"ἁρμοῖ","slug":"ἁρμοῖ","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>ἁρμοῖ</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>=<el>ἄρτι, ἀρτίως</el>\n<p/><i>just, newly, lately</i>, <b><a href='S:Aeschylus'>Aesch.</a></b>, <b><a href='S:Theocritus'>Theocr.</a></b><p/><br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>In fact, an old <a href='S:dative'>dat.</a> of <a href='S:ἁρμός'><el>ἁρμός</el></a>; <a href='S:confer, compare'>cf.</a> <el>οἴκοι, πέδοι.</el>\n"}]}